cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.DB. 

The paper deals with natural language generation from structured data, specifically tables. This falls under the category of natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) as it leverages the semantics of a table to generate natural language sentences. Finally, the paper introduces a new dataset (cs.DB) for open-domain table-to-text generation.
